		"content": {
			"start": 7,
			"end": 309,
			"styles": "\n\t/* @page block is agnostic: a nested style rule parses alongside declarations */\n\t@page :first {\n\t\th1 {\n\t\t\tcolor: red;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\t/* declarations, margin at-rules, and nested rules coexist in one @page block */\n\t@page {\n\t\tmargin: 1cm;\n\t\t@top-center {\n\t\t\tcontent: 'x';\n\t\t}\n\t\th1 {\n\t\t\tcolor: blue;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n",
